{"tid":558114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大平反][捷進行動]警方製造人為塞車 專用於追截賊車的戰術","createTime":"2018-02-12T03:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T05:07:59.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a93b867279a642a27f39e91a60fd47b3cd879dfc","tid":558114,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:41:50.000Z","msg":"「捷進行動」為警方專用於追截賊車的戰術，由警察指揮及控制中心統籌，目的是在交通繁忙的公路上製造人為塞車，阻截歹徒逃走，讓警方盡快趕至緝捕。<br />\n戰術分四級，由對可疑車輛只追不截，到派出多輛警車包圍可疑車輛，警方指揮控制中心會同時調派交通警員、巡警和衝鋒隊把守各交通要點，掌握可疑車輛去向，再知會交通部延長賊車採用路綫的紅燈時間，阻擋疑犯去路，甚至引導其往特定方向，使之陷入「前無去路、後有追兵」的天羅地網。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtaousa.com/日報/香港/371843-「捷進」製塞車-警阻賊車逃/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtaousa.com%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F371843-%E3%80%8C%E6%8D%B7%E9%80%B2%E3%80%8D%E8%A3%BD%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E9%98%BB%E8%B3%8A%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%83%2F&d=iwyn6yoGta3D5KB84zi1lP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=185ce14d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtaousa.com/日報/香港/371843-「捷進」製塞車-警阻賊車逃/</a><br />\n<br />\n各位小朋友見到未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想要賠償就去搵警務署啦，但戰術唔會有變lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪再大驚小怪小題大做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做"},{"pid":"04555d093de50253eeccb5fb214af26a2c7672cc","tid":558114,"uid":149041,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"咁係咪有問題呀？"},{"pid":"a9373347053ef36b82bbab090f0ccb9bae040907","tid":558114,"uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"04555d093de50253eeccb5fb214af26a2c7672cc","tid":558114,"uid":149041,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"咁係咪有問題呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:45:29.000Z","msg":"咁關警犬咩事<br />\n<br />\n怪就怪個賊自爆撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284a66831cfc2728a70b06dbefa6322e